skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my journal
des:
My Journal makes it easy to record your thoughts, or even just your mood, each day. Your entries are stored securely in the cloud and accessible only to you, and only via Alexa (email reports coming soon!). 

Tips to use My Journal:
- OPEN: "Alexa, open My Journal."
- ADD MOOD: "I feel great", "I feel tired" (starts with "I feel")
- ADD JOURNAL ENTRY: "Today I played basketball at the gym", "Today my friends took my out for my birthday" (starts with "Today")
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
